title: BISP Chairperson visits Quaidâ€™s mausoleum, pays homage
content:
KARACHI, May 19 (APP):The Chairperson, Benazir Income Support Program (BISP), Senator Rubina Khalid visited the mausoleum of father of the nation Quaid-e-Azam Mohammed Ali Jinnah and paid homage, here on Monday.
She laid a wreath and offered fateha. She also prayed for the development and prosperity of the country.
BISP Director General Sindh Zone Zulfikar Ali Shaikh was also present on the occasion.
